About
Secret GroupSecret Group
This group is for anyone enrolled in the University of Waterloo's Software Engineering Program ...(Class of 2018) - and upper year mentors as well.

All members can use this page to stay connected, have discussions and make new friends because after all, we'll be together for the next 5 years!

Share information, ask questions, make friends and make our class the best ever!! See More
